snippet.title: Nowhere Prophet Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Nowhere Prophet on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/681730/Nowhere_Prophet/

Nowhere Prophet is a the roguelike deck-building game set in a sci-fi post-apocalypse. Become the last hope to a band of outcastes and lead them across the randomly generated wastelands. 

More info: http://www.nowhereprophet.com
Sharkbomb Studios: http://www.sharkbombs.com
No More Robots: http://nomorerobots.io
